00:26:09,836 --> 00:26:16,129
deter you, should not stop you; for you
know that they are stupid,

236
00:26:16,329 --> 00:26:25,620
they are destructive and they will destroy
all the, all the good qualities.

237
00:26:26,168 --> 00:26:32,221
You should know that the responsibility
of Americans

238
00:26:32,422 --> 00:26:38,804
is much greater than the responsibility
of any other Sahaja yogis,

239
00:26:39,005 --> 00:26:46,274
because they are accepted and regarded

240
00:26:47,656 --> 00:27:03,945
as the most competent people, as the most
effective people by the divine Power.

241
00:27:04,146 --> 00:27:11,376
Divine Power thinks that now you can go
all ahead,

242
00:27:11,577 --> 00:27:15,907
you can do so much, and let us see.

243
00:27:16,107 --> 00:27:21,017
Like we have the power and the machinery,

244
00:27:21,218 --> 00:27:28,835
but the machinery if it doesn't work, what's
the use of the power? It is useless.

245
00:27:29,036 --> 00:27:36,334
So the machinery has to work, and it is
working, it is spreading,

246
00:27:36,535 --> 00:27:40,280
but we have to double our efforts.

247
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:45,392
I was thinking of doing some sort
of a social work here

248
00:27:45,593 --> 00:27:51,770
so that it will go, it will be caught
in the eyes of many people.

249
00:27:53,183 --> 00:27:57,836
On a subtler level we have worked,

250
00:28:20,799 --> 00:28:27,281
but now we have to work it on the surface.

251
00:28:27,481 --> 00:28:36,647
Subtler level we are there, we have
achieved and we can achieve much more.

252
00:28:36,848 --> 00:28:44,580
But we should come out of it and think
what can we do on the surface,

253
00:28:44,781 --> 00:28:52,943
so that people see what is Sahaja Yoga is,
and what it can do to people.

254
00:28:53,955 --> 00:29:03,444
It's your personal behavior, your collective
behavior, your national behavior,

255
00:29:03,645 --> 00:29:12,193
all are going to change the atmosphere
which is supposed to be superficial,

256
00:29:12,393 --> 00:29:16,607
so that that also becomes subtler.

257
00:29:16,807 --> 00:29:23,318
I've been saying this in many places, but
at this puja I think it is important to say

258
00:29:23,519 --> 00:29:27,181
that if you are really facing the Adi
Shakti,

259
00:29:27,382 --> 00:29:32,871
then you must know your powers are
boundless.

260
00:29:34,455 --> 00:29:40,007
You have to just assert those powers.

261
00:29:40,311 --> 00:29:46,203
It is not a stationary power. Itâ€™s, there's
a movement in it,

262
00:29:46,403 --> 00:29:49,837
and there's a right type of a movement.

263
00:29:50,037 --> 00:29:54,624
It knows where to enter, how to work it
out. Now look at this place.

264
00:29:54,824 --> 00:30:00,358
Can you imagine Me thinking about a place
like this?

265
00:30:00,559 --> 00:30:04,296
But I was just had in mind of course,
I must say,

266
00:30:04,496 --> 00:30:08,212
that we should have some place here,
because

267
00:30:08,413 --> 00:30:15,116
the American Sahaja yogis didn't have any
place to meet - that's all.

268
00:30:15,317 --> 00:30:18,285
And see how I got it!

269
00:30:18,485 --> 00:30:24,239
But the desire to do all this

270
00:30:24,439 --> 00:30:30,866
should be there within your subtler level,
and then it works.

271
00:30:31,067 --> 00:30:34,647
It works, it's like a magic, I tell you.

272
00:30:34,847 --> 00:30:40,843
Now you have faith in yourself and decide
about it.

273
00:30:41,044 --> 00:30:48,913
I am so very happy that it has been
achieved

274
00:30:49,113 --> 00:30:55,425
with such ease - unbelievable, with such
ease.

275
00:30:55,626 --> 00:31:01,662
Absolutely, nothing great was done.

276
00:31:01,862 --> 00:31:06,895
The way we got this was so simple,

277
00:31:07,095 --> 00:31:12,603
that just like another Sahaja yogi
the person was to sell us

278
00:31:12,804 --> 00:31:20,140
came down so excited, and he just sold it
to us, finished.

279
00:31:20,688 --> 00:31:26,232
We didn't have to do anything to convince
him

280
00:31:26,432 --> 00:31:33,696
or to talk to him or reduce the price -
nothing. And he sold it out to us.

281
00:31:33,897 --> 00:31:39,482
In the same way whatever on a subtler level
you desire,

282
00:31:39,682 --> 00:31:45,950
it becomes a terrific force which moves
by itself,

283
00:31:46,150 --> 00:31:57,251
which knows where to go, how to enter, into
which area, and it gets the thing done.

284
00:31:57,482 --> 00:32:06,541
It's something we all should experience,
and work it out with full confidence.

285
00:32:06,741 --> 00:32:12,396
It is the love that we have, the concern
we have.

286
00:32:12,596 --> 00:32:19,171
This is the power that has given us
Self-realization, and this is the power

287
00:32:19,371 --> 00:32:25,149
that has given us this enrichment
of achievements.

288
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:30,375
I am sure all of you who are here will
realize

289
00:32:30,575 --> 00:32:35,638
how it was done - I mean, so quickly.
This is one of the things

290
00:32:35,838 --> 00:32:44,357
that should just tell you what we are
capable of doing,

291
00:32:45,695 --> 00:32:48,684
what we are capable of achieving.

292
00:32:48,885 --> 00:32:58,037
And when you think of so many people who
are lost in the mire of ignorance,

293
00:32:58,237 --> 00:33:03,036
we should really feel from inside that
concern

294
00:33:03,237 --> 00:33:13,437
and that hankering, "How can I help these
people?"

295
00:33:13,762 --> 00:33:18,003
And you'll be amazed, once you think like
that,

296
00:33:18,204 --> 00:33:22,496
how this divine Power, this Force, will
come in.

297
00:33:22,696 --> 00:33:31,342
Forget about petty things and petty
problems, they're nothing.

298
00:33:31,542 --> 00:33:35,837
You have such a powerful thing behind you.

299
00:33:36,037 --> 00:33:41,709
It's true that all this universe was
created, everything was created

300
00:33:41,909 --> 00:33:45,002
and then you were created, and all that
is done.

301
00:33:45,202 --> 00:33:49,548
But the greatest thing this Power has done
is to create

302
00:33:49,748 --> 00:33:53,860
Sahaja yogis. This is the greatest thing.

303
00:33:54,060 --> 00:34:02,187
Those who have knowledge, those who have
the pure knowledge

304
00:34:02,388 --> 00:34:09,974
and those who have the divine love in their
heart,

305
00:34:10,175 --> 00:34:15,542
what a tremendous personality it is. Just
think of that,

306
00:34:15,742 --> 00:34:24,195
and you will get all the opportunities
to express that love.

307
00:34:24,395 --> 00:34:27,753
So may God bless you.

